API
 - An implementation in Bash for the Monitis REST API
RRD
 - Integration of Monitis with RRD systems, currently supporting only munin
 - Includes also a command line API for interacting with the REST API of Monitis
M3
 - M3 => MMM => Monitis Monitor Manager - A monitor manager for Monitis
   implemented in Perl and using the Monitis Perl-SDK
 - Includes the new DBI integration as well
